long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Change the background image on new tabs to feature cool Rally Racing related images! The extension also provides users with a Custom Web Search.

By installing "RallyRacingTab" extension, you agree to the EULA and Privacy Policy, and to set your new tab page to RallyRacingTab.

The new tab search features used within the extension will be 
provided by Microsoft Bing.
